      • setCapacity

        void setCapacity(int capacity)
        Sets the new size of this cache. If this cache already contains more items than the new capacity allows, items are discarded based on the cache policy.
        Parameters:
        capacity - the maximum number of entries in this cache.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the capacity is negative.
        UnsupportedOperationException - if this cache has a fixed size and does not support changing its capacity.

      • setPersistent

        void setPersistent(boolean persistent)
        Sets the persistence of this cache.
        Parameters:
        persistent - the new persistence of this cache.
        Throws:
        UnsupportedOperationException - if this cache does not support persistence.
